{{vgname|热力纳斯卡 进化|en=NASCAR Heat Evolution}}是即将推出的[[竞速游戏|竞速游戏]]，由[[怪兽游戏|怪兽游戏]]开发，Dusenberry Martin Racing发行。游戏预定于2016年9月登陆[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]、[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]和[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]。这是自2015年《[[纳斯卡'15_胜利版|纳斯卡'15 胜利版]]》的首款纳斯卡主题游戏，也是怪兽游戏自2002年《[[纳斯卡：Dirt_to_Daytona|纳斯卡：Dirt to Daytona]]》以来的首度开发拿斯卡游戏。

== 玩法 ==

游戏将收录[[2016納斯卡賽車斯普林特盃系列賽|2016納斯卡賽車斯普林特盃系列賽]]计划的全部赛道和部分车辆。《热力纳斯卡 进化》还有匹配玩家技术水平的动态[[人工智能|AI]]和速度评价系统。游戏有快速竞速、职业、夺杯和挑战四种模式。玩家在挑战模式用要达到或打破当前[[全國運動汽車競賽協會|纳斯卡]]记录<ref name="gamespot">{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/first-nascar-game-for-ps4-xbox-one-announced/1100-6440007/|title=First NASCAR Game for PS4, Xbox One Announced|date=2016-05-20|last=Makuch|first=Eddie|publisher=CBS Interactive|website=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|access-date=2016-05-20|archive-date=2016-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160527092604/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/first-nascar-game-for-ps4-xbox-one-announced/1100-6440007/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 开发 ==

Dusenberry Martin Racing（当时称DMi Games）2015年收购了Eutechnyx<ref name="GI DMi" />，获得到2020年的纳斯卡授权<ref name="NASCAR.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.nascar.com/en_us/news-media/articles/2016/5/20/dusenberry-martin-racing-nascar-heat-contest.html|title=Dusenberry Martin Racing announces NASCAR Heat Evolution|website=NASCAR.com|publisher=NASCAR Media Group, LLC.|date=2016-05-20|accessdate=2016-05-20|archive-date=2017-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170811111738/http://www.nascar.com/en_us/news-media/articles/2016/5/20/dusenberry-martin-racing-nascar-heat-contest.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。公司总裁艾德·马丁之前就职于[[Papyrus_Design_Group|Papyrus Design Group]]、[[Hasbro互动|Hasbro互动]]、[[EA_Sports|EA Sports]]和Eutechnyx，为各公司分别开发了《纳斯卡竞速》、《热力拿斯卡》、EA Sports纳斯卡作品以及《纳斯卡 游戏》。CEO汤姆·杜森伯里是Hasbro互动的创办人兼总裁<ref name="GI DMi">{{cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2015/01/19/new-company-gets-exclusive-nascar-rights.aspx|title=New Company Gets Exclusive NASCAR Rights|accessdate=2016-05-20|date=2015-01-19|last=Kato|first=Matthew|publisher=''[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]''|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126132106/https://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2015/01/19/new-company-gets-exclusive-nascar-rights.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

Dusenberry Martin Racing于5月20日正式宣布，将和《热力纳斯卡》和《纳斯卡：Dirt to Daytona》开发商怪兽游戏合作，开发[[夏洛特赛道|夏洛特赛道]]的游戏。怪兽游戏总裁理查德·加西亚是该作总开发人，他曾是《热力纳斯卡》设计团队的一员<ref name="polygonann">{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2016/5/20/11719046/nascar-heat-evolution-xbox-one-ps4-launch-date-september-13|title=NASCAR makes current-gen console debut this fall with NASCAR Heat Evolution|accessdate=2016-05-20|date=2016-05-20|publisher=Vox Media|last1=Good|first1=Owen S.|website=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109044038/http://www.polygon.com/2016/5/20/11719046/nascar-heat-evolution-xbox-one-ps4-launch-date-september-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Dusenberry Martin Racing聘请赛手[[Joey_Logano|Joey Logano]]、[[Ryan_Blaney|Ryan Blaney]]和[[Brad_Keselowski|Brad Keselowski]]协助游戏开发。封面车手在斯普林特全明星赛中，排名最高车队丰田中选出<ref>{{cite web|last=Jensen|first=Tom|url=http://www.foxsports.com/nascar/story/dusenberry-martin-racing-nascar-heat-evolution-sprint-cup-series-charlotte-motor-speedway-052016|title=Dusenberry Martin Racing to unveil new NASCAR video game|website=[[Foxsports.com|Foxsports.com]]|publisher=[[Fox_Sports_Digital_Media|Fox Sports Digital Media]]|date=2016-05-20|accessdate=2016-05-20|location=[[Concord,_North_Carolina|Concord, North Carolina]]|archive-date=2018-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180910094728/https://www.foxsports.com/nascar/story/dusenberry-martin-racing-nascar-heat-evolution-sprint-cup-series-charlotte-motor-speedway-052016|dead-url=no}}</ref>，候选车手有[[Kyle_Busch|Kyle Busch]]、[[Carl_Edwards|Carl Edwards]]、[[Denny_Hamlin|Denny Hamlin]]、[[Matt_Kenseth|Matt Kenseth]]和[[Martin_Truex_Jr.|Martin Truex Jr.]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2016/05/20/monster-games-returns-with-nascar-heat-evolution.aspx|title=Monster Games Returns With NASCAR Heat Evolution|accessdate=2016-05-20|date=2016-05-20|last=Kato|first=Matthew|publisher=''[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]''|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414223302/https://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2016/05/20/monster-games-returns-with-nascar-heat-evolution.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>，排名第四的Edwards最终获选<ref name="Edwards">{{cite web|url=http://www.nascar.com/en_us/news-media/articles/2016/5/22/carl-edwards-rallies-lug-nut-penalty-sprint-all-star-race-charlotte.html|title=Carl Edwards rallies from miscues for top-five spot|accessdate=2016-05-22|date=2016-05-22|last=Albert|first=Zack|publisher=NASCAR Media Group, LLC.|website=NASCAR.com|location=[[Concord,_North_Carolina|Concord, North Carolina]]|archive-date=2017-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305023545/http://www.nascar.com/en_us/news-media/articles/2016/5/22/carl-edwards-rallies-lug-nut-penalty-sprint-all-star-race-charlotte.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这时第八世代游戏机上的首款纳斯卡作品，对应PlayStation 4和Xbox One<ref name="polygonann" />。

